    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，INIT_HW失败要进入FAULT状态。另外从IDLE可以响应两种命令：EV_CMD_ARM进入ARMED预启动状态，或者直接EV_CMD_START进入RAMP_UP升压过程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IDLE",
        "ARMED",
        "RAMP_UP",
        "EV_CMD_ARM",
        "EV_CMD_START"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把ARMED也加上RAMP_UP的转换，这样预启动后也能START。还有ARMED应该能退回IDLE吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARMED",
